                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#108">Fol. 108</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note, written in the main hand, states that Gäbrä Ḥǝywät purchased and donated the book to the church of Qirqos ʿAddigrat gädam in 1931 A.M. (= 1938/39 A.D.). It mentions also the names of his family members.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ተአምረ፡ ማርያም is written on fol. 1r with red modern paint.&#xD;
- Pen trial: fol. 107r.</item>
                     </list>
